{
  "texts": [
    "Proactive maintenance substantially enhances network reliability and stability by minimizing emergency repairs and replacement costs.",
    "O&M in advance plays a crucial role in resource allocation and management optimization.",
    "Moreover, predicting user demand and network load allows for dynamic resource distribution adjustments.",
    "This proactive approach ensures that high-quality service is consistently maintained even during peak usage periods, which enhances user satisfaction and reduces operational costs.",
    "O&M in advance also accelerates the deployment and validation of new technologies."
  ]
}